The application was written in java 11 and requires at least this version
The application reads data from the local database.
Before using it, you must configure it for this purpose:
1. open file src\main\resources\hibernate.cfg.xml
2 in  line 18 jdbc:h2:file:.....  you must enter database location
3 right click on db.mv.db and chose copy patch
4 past it in jdbc:h2:file:... for example jdbc:h2:file:C:\programowanie\!HOME_TODO_LIST\TODO\db remember to delete .mv.db
After that you can open your browser and visit site http://localhost:8080/